  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU</h1><p><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494720/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1688654652\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494720/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1688654652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494720/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1688654652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494720/extras/6e77186ffd28307077fc5647f014ed1d.avif?t=1688654652\" width=572 height=138 /></span><br><br>Astronauts beyond the stars we know are looking for a path, and you will help them to find it.<br><br><i>Mini Moves: Among Stars</i> is a point and click puzzle game. You will solve puzzles to put all the astronauts in the right place with limited moves and other new challenges according with your progress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494720/extras/71f277615e272d0e4a80c2ea1564d343.poster.avif?t=1688654652\" width=572 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494720/extras/71f277615e272d0e4a80c2ea1564d343.webm?t=1688654652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494720/extras/71f277615e272d0e4a80c2ea1564d343.mp4?t=1688654652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FEATURES </strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple Controls<br></li><li>40 levels<br></li><li>Relaxing graphics and sounds<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494720/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1688654652\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494720/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1688654652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494720/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1688654652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
